  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.9.1">
<l>ivaiyu mavaiyu muvaiyu mivaru mavaru muvaru</l>
<l>mavaiyum yavaruntaṉ ṉuḷḷē yākiyu mākkiyuṅ kākku</l>
<l>mavaiyu ṭaṉimuta lemmāṉ kaṇṇa pirāṉeṉ ṉamutañ</l>
<l>cuvaiyaṉ ṟiruviṉ maṇāḷa ṉeṉṉuṭaic cūḻalu ḷāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who guards inside himself, becoming and creating [them], those things and people:</l>
<l>these things, the things there, those things, this people, the people there, those people</l>
<l>the sole cause among those, our lord,  lord Kaṇṇaṉ, my one with the taste</l>
<l>of ambrosia, the husband of Śrī, he is inside my mind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
